Great recipe although I only used ground beef because that's all I had on hand. I was puzzled by the high temperature to cook this dish but once it came out of the oven I understood that this is what makes the meatloaf so crispy good. Served with my homemade salsa. Can wait for tomorrow's meatloaf sandwich. Yum!

