Great recipe. Try topping (last 5 mins of cooking) with 50-50 catsup and Makers Mark Gourmet Sauce. Not a sauce to cook with. I have also used carrots, onion, seasoned bread crumbs, and garlic in a processor in place of oats.

Rating: 2
Having read other reviewers' comments about dryness, I added 2 eggs (I tripled the recipe for 6) - it was satisfying moist. However, I thought this was neither "fish nor fowl", i.e., it really wasn't Swedish meatballs in a loaf form, nor was it that wonderful a "traditional" meatloaf (the mustard was a nice touch and the sauce worked okay).

