Rating: 3
Super good and easy to make. I didn't have rye bread, so I used regular bread crumbs. (I think 2/3 cup is a bit too much.) I served the meat loaf with the dill sauce, creamed spinach and steamed carrots as suggested and my husband and I really enjoyed this as a mid-week dinner combo.

