Very tasty and easy. I substituted ground turkey for the pork and increased the amount of mustard and dill for extra flavor. This one received rave reviews and it changed my mind about meat loaf being boring.

Rating: 3
This recipe is easy and delicious. We were not big fans of meatloaf before, but with this recipe we really enjoy it. I have made it several times and it never gets boring.

Rating: 3
This was very very very nice and incredibly simple to make. I doubled the recipe for the three of us and had enough leftover to eat for lunch at work! And the flavor of the leftover was just as nice as fresh cooked! The small size of each 'loaf' was perfect as the time for cooking was decreased, a great recipe if you need to whip something up during the week. I've passed this one on to lots of others already. Yum Yum Yum!